lamb cassoulet

Soak 500g broad beans dried overnight.

Fry lamb shoulder (2kg ish) in chunks
Add dried oregano, 2 onions, 2 carrots chopped, 2 celery chopped, 1 bay leaf, 10 cl garlic. cover with water to cover meat.  simmer 1 hour or 2 hours at 160 in oven.
Meanwhile peal broadbeans, and cook together another hour (can preshed the lamb).
